title: Lunchbox
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Mediterranean, Fast food, Delivery, Take-out, Kosher, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Offers healthier food boxed for take out, or eat on the premises. Includes vegan options in each category: mains, lunch, desserts, sides, salads, sandwiches. The ingredients and nutritional information are marked each box. Daily deals are posted. Ask for a lunch coupon with your first order; the 10th lunch is free.
